<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:83215">
				
    <ab xml:lang="san-Latn" rendition="class:grantha maturity:83215">
        <lb n="1"/>svasti śrī
    </ab>
    <p>Ariṇa Uṭaiyārkku cellā niṉṟa <unclear>tu</unclear>mtumi varu
        
        <lb n="2" break="no"/><hi rend="bold">ṣa</hi>m tai mātam mutal tiyati
    </p>
    <p>
        valliyūr Uṭaiyār ma<supplied reason="omitted">ṇ</supplied>ṇai-nāyanār
        <lb n="3"/>k<choice><orig>o</orig><reg>ō</reg></choice>yil tānattār<choice><orig>o</orig><reg>ō</reg></choice>m Iṉ-ṉāyanār <unclear>ti</unclear>ru-maṭai-viḷākattil
        
        <lb n="4"/><unclear>ka</unclear>varipiṇā poṟk<choice><orig>o</orig><reg>ō</reg></choice>yil kaikk<choice><orig>o</orig><reg>ō</reg></choice>ḷaṟakku Aṟu<unclear>ti</unclear> paṇṇi-k kuṭutta
        
        <lb n="5"/><unclear>paṭi</unclear>
    </p>
    
    <p>
        Iv-ūr valaṅkai Iṭaṅkai ciluk' āy nālu-varu<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>m pāḻ-<unclear>ki</unclear>ṭakkaiyil
        <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="omitted">ku</supplied>ṭi Ēṟa-k-kaṭavarkaḷ Ākavum
    </p>
    
    <p>        
        kuṭi Ēṟi Iṭattu taṟi-k-kaṭamai-vācal paṇam
        
        <lb n="7"/>Aiñcu paṇam koḷḷa-k-kaṭavatu Ākavum
    </p>
    
    <p>        
        paṭṭaṭai nāṇayattuku pattil
        
        <lb n="8"/>Aiñcu māṉiyattu Āṇṭu Oṉṟukku taṟi Oṉṟukku Oru paṇam ko<unclear>ḷḷavum</unclear>
    </p>
    
    <p>        
        <lb n="9"/>maṟṟum Uḷḷa cakala Upātikaḷum Uṭpaṭa Āṇṭ’ oṉṟukku taṟi Oṉṟukku     
    </p>
</div>
	
<div type="translation" resp="part:doop">
		
    <p n="1">
        Prosperity! Fortune!		
    </p>
    
    <p>...</p>
    
